'''{{ill|Kin-gū|ja|金武宮|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kin-gū|qq=}}''' (金武宮, Kin-gū) is a [[:en:Shinto shrine|Shinto shrine]] located in [[Kin Town]], [[Kunigami District]], [[:en:Okinawa Prefecture|Okinawa Prefecture]], Japan. It is one of the {{ill|Eight Ryukyu Shrines|ja|琉球八社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eight Ryukyu Shrines|qq=}}<ref name=":0">https://www.goteamjosh.com/blog/tag/Eight+Shrines+of+Okinawa</ref> and was an unranked shrine in the [[Modern system of Ranked Shinto shrines|Meiji period]].

